item.title: 163 Canning Road, KALAMUNDA WA 6076
item.dc:creator: eplcoretest-admin
item.content:encoded:
A unique blend of old and new, this wonderful 4x1 hills home on 1000sqm block is the perfect combination of cottage charm with a modern finish.
Featuring a new modern kitchen and a fantastic open plan living area including a wood fire place for those cold winter nights. Being freshly painted and with new carpet throughout, there is nothing for you to do, just move in!
Here you are well set back from the road with plenty of open parking and easy side access to the rear large powered workshop. The 1000sqm block has all the room you desire for a growing family or a growing car collection. Well located with a short drive to shops, schools and being right outside the bus route its easy to get around without a car.
The finer details include-
*New modern kitchen with plenty cupboard space opening into family room *New carpets to the 4 bedrooms, activity and living areas. *Ducted evaporated air-conditioning, refrigerated split unit and a wood fire heater. *Spacious open plan lounge and meals area. *Recently painted inside and out. *Large powered workshop & locked garage with plenty of outdoor parking space through the easy side access. *Large front yard with freshly laid grass. *Additional toilet.

item.title: 10 Fernan Rd, HIGH WYCOMBE WA 6057
item.dc:creator: eplcoretest-admin
item.content:encoded:
This fully renovated 3x2 home sits on a 399sqm street front strata block, having the perfect blend of modern features with classic charm.
A cosy and compact home that would suit the first home buyer or downsizer who wants to get into the market and prefers quality finishing over a big house size. Here you will have no strata fees and nothing to do for you to move in.
You are ideally located a short walk to the High Wycombe town centre with plenty of shopping and food options on your door step. Handy to both airports, 20min drive to the city and a short walk to the bus stop.
The finer details include-
*Compact, well presented home. *Stunning polished boards to the kitchen and living area. *New carpets, blinds and freshly painted throughout. *Two separate living zones with the front lounge and enclosed back patio. *Back courtyard covered with a shade sail. *Well presented kitchen with good cupboard space. *Split system air conditioning. *Front and back security screen doors. *Modern main bathroom with glass shower screen and shower over bath tub. *Second bathroom/laundry with shower and separate toilet. *Double car parking bays. *Fully Restored roof restoration. *Easy care gardens. *399sqm street front strata block with no strata fees.

item.title: 12 Westralia Gardens, ROCKINGHAM WA 6168
item.dc:creator: eplcoretest-admin
item.content:encoded:
The City of Rockingham is a seaside location about 50km south of the Perth CBD. Rockingham contains two major shopping districts with the city centre precinct only walking distance from the Lakeview Apartments.
Growth Prospects- Rockingham is continuously mentioned as an area earmarked for huge capital growth and featured in the attached National Top 10 Best Buys 2013 (page 78) and 2014' by hotspotting.com.au and the 2012 & 2013 Fast 50 Report from leading property resource Smart Property Investment.
Rockingham is experiencing huge population growth for its affordability, beachside lifestyle, exceptional facilities, direct train access to Perth CBD. The area also isn't reliant on the mining industry.
The Location- Lakeview Apartments are located within the picturesque City Park which boasts 2 lakes, kids playground, picnic facilities and stunning water features. The development is less than 2km from Rockingham Beach and 400m from Rockingham City Shopping Centre a major hub within Rockingham containing 215 stores.
The area is serviced by the Rockingham Train Station on the Mandurah Line connected to Rockingham with a high frequency 15 minute shuttle service between the new Rockingham Train Station and the beachfront.
The Development- These modern and chic one & two bedroom apartments are available from $315,000 and are built to a high specification. Each apartment block within Stage 1 & 2 will provide lift access for residents, private balconies, allocated parking and some with stunning views of City Park.
Pricing- 1x1's From $315,000 2x1's & 2x2's From $370,000
Finance & Deposits- Contracts are Cash Unconditional and are not Subject to Finance. Purchasers are required to pay $1000 deposit upon signing the contract and the balance of a 10% deposit is payable within 21 days of the contract date.
For full info pack containing specifications, pricing and plans please submit an enquiry below or phone Investors Edge on 9472 1606.

item.content:encoded:

item.title: 52 Caledonian Ave, MAYLANDS WA 6051
item.dc:creator: eplcoretest-admin
item.content:encoded:
The Avenues offers a boutique apartment building located on the river side of Guildford Road in Maylands.
The Location- Darby Apartments' location, between the peace of the Swan River and the bustle of Guildford Road, will provide residents with the best of urban living. The Good Food Guide names numerous Maylands restaurants and cafes as amongst the best in Perth, particularly on the Eighth Ave Strip which is just 1km away whilst the tranquillity of the river and its related reserves offers rare convenience to recreational spaces.
The Development- Consisting of just 8 apartments, four one bedroom one bathroom and four two bedroom two bathroom apartments. This 2 bedroom 2 bathroom ground floor apartment will offer residents contemporary, affordable and stylish living. Fitted out to a very high standard and on completion just move in..and enjoy the city and river on your doorstep
Pricing- 1x1 Apartments $388,000 expected rent $380-420pw. 2x2 Apartments $495,000 expected rent of $450-$490pw.
The Specifications- *Reverse cycle air conditioning *European stainless steel appliances *Dishwasher and clothes dryer *Engineered stone bench tops *Higher than standard ceilings *Timber flooring *Secure undercover parking *Lockable storage room *Window treatments *Range of colour schemes
Finance & Deposits- Contracts are Cash Unconditional and are not Subject to Finance. Purchasers are required to pay $1000 deposit upon signing the contract and the balance of a 10% deposit is payable within 21 days of the contract date.
For full info pack containing specifications, pricing and plans please submit an enquiry below or phone Jarrad Mahon or Anthony Tran at Investors Edge on 9472 1606.
